{"tid":1447190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［一齊煲大佢］要班黑警狗官血債血償","createTime":"2019-08-11T15:40:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:11:33.000Z","uid":119623,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"26fa1f8b34eb6f0577b4e67beeede98ac15fd613","tid":1447190,"uid":119623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:40:29.000Z","msg":"必定要逐一煲大黑警做過嘅事，推畀全世界見到。<br />\n<br />\n1. 用過期催淚彈<br />\n2. 瞄準示威者要害位置來發射子彈<br />\n3. 假扮示威者<br />\n4. 721事件 警黑合作<br />\n5. 室內射tear gas<br />\n6. 沒有警告下施行武力<br />\n7. 警方不肯出示委任證<br />\n8. 中國公安假裝香港警察<br />\n9. 對記者進行武力行為<br />\n10. 阻礙記者拍攝<br />\n<br />\n仲有好多好多，想大家一次過打曬出黎、整理好資料，一齊煲大佢。<br />\n班狗官到而家從來未正面回應過我地訴求。黑警狗官你地一定要血債血償，不得好死。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span><br />\n- 撤回逃犯條例<br />\n- 撤回暴動定義<br />\n- 撤回所有抗爭者控罪<br />\n- 追究警隊濫權<br />\n- 立即實行雙普選<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港   時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n佢地越係要我地驚，我地越要企硬！"},{"pid":"c48d99b9089ef48eee6581ca8c6a24d91343d8b2","tid":1447190,"uid":119623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:43:12.000Z","msg":"班狗官有黑警做佢地既CONDOM，所以一直遲遲未肯回應。我地必須整穿呢個CONDOM，射到佢地一面都係。"},{"pid":"eb4ee42364880cbdda7fcb4832536bd8950c610d","tid":1447190,"uid":178933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:44:09.000Z","msg":"煲大佢"},{"pid":"58a3f22bb96f11c3f8c6f9103feada0074f4264f","tid":1447190,"uid":119623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:50:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">血債血償</span></span>"},{"pid":"aad872f4a92e7b00b6fbb0858e684dc51569fd1b","tid":1447190,"uid":299476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:51:41.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"2c0f8d2714b5742ece42f8d9e32ab6374ec128bf","tid":1447190,"uid":119623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:52:52.000Z","msg":"<a